ZH: 我家雇了一个佣人来打扫房子。
EN: We hired a maid to clean the house.

ZH: 那个佣人每天做饭给我们吃。
EN: The servant cooks for us every day.

ZH: 我们家的佣人很有礼貌。
EN: Our household help is very polite.

ZH: 她是一个勤劳的佣人。
EN: She is a hardworking domestic worker.

ZH: 请问你们有佣人的工作经验吗？
EN: Do you have any experience as a servant?

ZH: 我希望将来可以雇个佣人帮忙。
EN: I hope to hire a helper in the future.

ZH: 他们雇佣了一名新的佣人来照顾孩子。
EN: They hired a new servant to take care of their children.

ZH: 我佣了一个家政服务公司来洗衣服。
EN: I hired a housekeeping service company to do the laundry.

ZH: 我朋友在家里雇了四名佣人。
EN: My friend has hired four servants at home.

ZH: 最近找到一份当佣人的工作。
EN: I recently found a job as a maid.

ZH: 这家旅馆的佣人都很友好。
EN: The hotel staff are all very friendly.

ZH: 她的梦想是做一名佣人。
EN: Her dream is to become a household helper.

ZH: 我请了一位佣人帮我打扫房间。
EN: I hired a house helper to clean my room.

ZH: 佣人是这家照料老人的机构的一员。
EN: The servant is a member of this elderly care institution.

ZH: 我们聘请的佣人来自菲律宾。
EN: Our hired household help comes from the Philippines.

ZH: 这位佣人总是按时完成所有的家务。
EN: This servant always completes all the household chores on time.

ZH: 她雇了一名临时佣人来帮忙。
EN: She hired a temporary servant to help out.

ZH: 雇主应该尊重佣人的权益。
EN: Employers should respect the rights of domestic workers.

ZH: 这个佣人家庭从事这一工作已有十年了。
EN: This household helper has been in this job for ten years.

ZH: 她是一名专业的佣人，擅长烹饪和清洁。
EN: She is a professional servant, skilled in cooking and cleaning.
